data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This well maintained 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and elegance. Three spacious bedrooms, including the master suite, are situated upstairs, while a convenient fourth bedroom is located downstairs for added flexibility.  Enjoy the warmth of family gatherings in the separate dining room and unwind in the generously sized family room with stone fireplace. A well-appointed kitchen opens to the family room and is complemented by a huge laundry room, ensuring both style and functionality. A sunroom and a separate office provide versatile spaces for work or relaxation.  Step outside to discover over an acre of private land highlighted by a huge front porch and a large deck for outdoor enjoyment. The property boasts a two-car carport for your convenience. All appliances, including the washer, dryer, and refrigerator, are included.  With its ideal location close to town, this residence offers the perfect combination of tranquility and accessibility. Don't miss the opportunity to call this charming property your new home!
